rows.label: tlk43700241_02_msg0001
rows.name:
I lost to you because I wasn't
using my Assist Cores properly.

rows.label: tlk43700241_02_msg0002
rows.name:
You know how there's one
called Damage Heal?

rows.label: tlk43700241_02_msg0003
rows.name:
If you equip that, then every
time you get attacked, you
get a portion of HP back.

rows.label: tlk43700241_02_msg0004
rows.name:
If the Holy Grail ever decided to fight
me again, I'd be able to stand up to her
now without being such a pushover!
